        Constructor for a meal with parameters.
        Parameters:
        strMeal - name of the meal
        idMeal - id of the meal
        strCategory - the category name
        strArea - the area name
        strTags - the tags associated with the meal
        strIngredients - the ingredients of the meal
        strMeasures - the measurements of the ingredients
        strSource - the name of the source
        strMealThumb - the meal thumb information
        strYoutube - a youtube tutorial link to make the meal
        strInstructions - instructions to make the meal
